---
import openaiLogo from "../../assets/OpenAI_light.svg";
import claudeLogo from "../../assets/claude-ai.svg";
import geminiLogo from "../../assets/google-gemini.svg";
import ollamaLogo from "../../assets/ollama.svg";
import openRouterLogo from "../../assets/open-router.svg";
import rustLogo from "../../assets/rust.svg";
---

<section class="ft-section" id="features" data-reveal>
	<p class="label">FEATURES</p>
	<h2>Everything you need,<br />nothing you don't</h2>
	<p class="section-sub">Built for writers and thinkers who want power without bloat.</p>

	<div class="feature-showcase">
		<div class="feature-showcase__grid">
			<div class="feature-showcase__row feature-showcase__row--duo">
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--hero">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-quill-write-02 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Markdown-first. Just write</h3>
					<p>A calm editor with slash commands, live preview, and helpful formatting tools. Every note is a plain .md file you keep and control.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-md-stack" aria-hidden="true">
							<div class="feature-md-chip feature-md-chip--one">
								<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-calendar-03"></i>
								archive.md
							</div>
							<div class="feature-md-chip feature-md-chip--two">
								<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-grid-table"></i>
								project.md
							</div>
							<div class="feature-md-chip feature-md-chip--three">
								<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-quill-write-02"></i>
								note.md
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--hero">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-ai-brain-04 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>AI that works with your notes</h3>
					<p>Summarize, draft, and ask questions using your notes as context. Works with your ChatGPT account, OpenAI, Anthropic, OpenRouter or local models via Ollama.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-ai-stack" aria-hidden="true">
							<div class="feature-ai-pill">
								<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-ai-brain-04"></i>
								Generate summary...
							</div>
							<div class="feature-ai-providers">
								<span class="feature-ai-provider feature-ai-provider--openai">
									<img src={openaiLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
								</span>
								<span class="feature-ai-provider feature-ai-provider--claude">
									<img src={claudeLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
								</span>
								<span class="feature-ai-provider feature-ai-provider--gemini">
									<img src={geminiLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
								</span>
								<span class="feature-ai-provider feature-ai-provider--openrouter">
									<img src={openRouterLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
								</span>
								<span class="feature-ai-provider feature-ai-provider--ollama">
									<img src={ollamaLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-showcase__row feature-showcase__row--quad">
				<article class="feature-showcase__card">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-link-03 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Linked notes that make sense</h3>
					<p>Connect ideas with [[wikilinks]] and instantly see backlinks. Your notes build a web of context as you think.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-link-pill" aria-hidden="true">
							<span class="feature-link-pill__bracket">[[</span>
							<span class="feature-link-pill__word">ideas</span>
							<span class="feature-link-pill__bracket">]]</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-task-01 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Notes, tasks, and boards</h3>
					<p>Structured views without a separate app. Tables, kanban boards, and task lists, all built from your notes and properties.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-kanban" aria-hidden="true">
							<div class="feature-kanban__col">
								<span class="feature-kanban__item feature-kanban__item--rose"></span>
								<span class="feature-kanban__item feature-kanban__item--blue"></span>
							</div>
							<div class="feature-kanban__col">
								<span class="feature-kanban__item feature-kanban__item--green"></span>
							</div>
							<div class="feature-kanban__col">
								<span class="feature-kanban__item feature-kanban__item--gold"></span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-search-01 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Search that keeps up</h3>
					<p>Press ⌘P and find notes by title, tag, folder, or full text in seconds.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-keys" aria-hidden="true">
							<span class="feature-keys__key">⌘</span>
							<span class="feature-keys__key">P</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-shield-key feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Private by default</h3>
					<p>Your notes stay on your Mac. No forced account, no surprise uploads.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-private-pill" aria-hidden="true">
							<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-shield-key"></i>
							Local only
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-showcase__row feature-showcase__row--compact">
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--compact">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-paint-board feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Themes</h3>
					<p>Colors, fonts, shortcuts.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-theme-deck" aria-hidden="true">
							<span class="feature-theme-swatch"></span>
							<span class="feature-theme-swatch"></span>
							<span class="feature-theme-swatch"></span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--compact">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-calendar-03 feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Daily notes</h3>
					<p>Calendar built in.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-calendar-pill" aria-hidden="true">Today</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--compact">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-grid-table feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>Collections</h3>
					<p>Tables and boards from tags.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-tags" aria-hidden="true">
							<span class="feature-tags__tag feature-tags__tag--blue">#work</span>
							<span class="feature-tags__tag feature-tags__tag--gold">#ideas</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--compact">
					<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-eye feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
					<h3>File preview</h3>
					<p>Images, PDFs, inline.</p>
					<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
						<div class="feature-files" aria-hidden="true">
							<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-eye feature-files__icon feature-files__icon--front"></i>
							<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-grid-table feature-files__icon feature-files__icon--back"></i>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
			<article class="feature-showcase__card feature-showcase__card--compact">
				<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-git-merge feature-showcase__icon" aria-hidden="true"></i>
				<h3>Git sync</h3>
				<p>Version history built in.</p>
				<div class="feature-showcase__flare">
					<div class="feature-git-pill" aria-hidden="true">
						<i class="hgi-stroke hgi-git-merge feature-git-pill__icon"></i>
						<span class="feature-git-pill__status">Tracked</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
			</div>
			<div class="feature-showcase__footer">
				<div class="feature-showcase__footer-brand">
					<div class="feature-showcase__footer-icon">
						<img src={rustLogo.src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3>Built with Rust</h3>
						<p>No Electron, no bloat.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="feature-showcase__footer-tags" aria-hidden="true">
					<span class="is-struck">Electron</span>
					<span>Native &amp; fast</span>
					<span>Instant launch</span>
					<span>~25 MB app</span>
					<span class="is-pill">macOS 15+</span>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<p class="ft-coda">Plus frontmatter properties, Mermaid diagrams, image embeds, and <a href="https://docs.glyphformac.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">plenty more</a>.</p>
</section>

<section class="section" data-reveal>
	<p class="label">DESIGN</p>
	<h2>Obsessively crafted</h2>
	<p class="section-sub">A native macOS app built by a solo developer who sweats the details. Every pixel, every shortcut, every transition.</p>
</section>
